Q35:
We are asking you to join a research study intended to understand the public’s preferences for different non-pharmaceutical interventions during pandemics. Study activities will include watching a four-minute video introducing the study and completing a 10-minute survey about your preferences and some background information about you. All of your responses will be anonymous and confidential. We do not expect any risks from taking part in this study. Participating in this study is voluntary. You are free to choose not to take part in this study. You also can change your mind and withdraw from the study at any time.  If you have any questions about the study, please contact Rachel Murray-Watson at rachel.murray-watson@yale.edu.
